<item>
            <title>[LU-1497] Lustre client build on SLES SP0 is broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1497</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To test some changes I did for another ticket I had to pull out my old SuSE SP0 client build environment for testing. In the process the builds failed for Lustre master branch as well as Lustre 2.2.0 branch. Patches are available for fixing these problems. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre client running a SLES SP0 environment.</environment>
        <key id="14815">LU-1497</key>
