                            <comment id="40432" author="simmonsja" created="Tue, 12 Jun 2012 12:29:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch for Lustre 2.2 is at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3065&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3065&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="40287" author="simmonsja" created="Fri, 8 Jun 2012 13:43:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch is at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3063&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3063&lt;/a&gt; for master.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="40286" author="pjones" created="Fri, 8 Jun 2012 13:25:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks James. Officially we only support SLES11 SP1 clients and make no attempt to build/test SLES11 SP0 so I am not surprised to learn that there are problems.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
